'''''Agara''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]]. Transporting repair kits along with a group of other civilian vessels, the ship was attacked by the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|Imperial Star Destroyer]] [[Emancipator|''Accuser'']] and the [[Immobilizer 418 Interdictor-class Heavy Cruiser|Immobilizer 418 cruiser]] [[Grappler (Immobilizer 418 cruiser)|''Grappler'']].

When the Interdictor was driven out by [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] in [[X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]] and [[A-wing]]s, all of the ships made a run for their [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] junctions through the fire of the ''Accuser''.

